metadata.name: Limitations #1/5
metadata.description:
Your only limit is you... it's a shout out to all the people who believed in you and helped you to break free from your limitations even if it's unknown, scary, hard..

Birds on the painting symbolise freedom, your goals, your dreams, the future you, and the ropes are your own limitations set by you..  

1/5 Collectors Special Edition
